00:04:00.365 --> 00:04:01.199 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Wow.

00:04:01.199 --> 00:04:03.577 align:middle line:84%
>>D'AGOSTINO: So we developed
that technology and also

00:04:03.577 --> 00:04:06.580 align:middle line:84%
