00:57:25.400 --> 00:57:26.902 align:middle line:90%
There's every kind of--

00:57:26.902 --> 00:57:28.487 align:middle line:90%
>>D'AGOSTINO: Yeah.

00:57:28.487 --> 00:57:35.786 align:middle line:84%
