00:58:06.608 --> 00:58:07.567 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Natural,
organic, and so forth.

00:58:07.567 --> 00:58:08.360 align:middle line:90%
>>D'AGOSTINO: Yes.

00:58:08.360 --> 00:58:10.862 align:middle line:84%
