00:59:10.839 --> 00:59:12.591 align:middle line:90%
>>D'AGOSTINO: OK.

00:59:12.591 --> 00:59:15.427 align:middle line:84%
The ones that are
most potent right now

00:59:15.427 --> 00:59:16.553 align:middle line:90%
are the ketone esters.

00:59:16.553 --> 00:59:21.099 align:middle line:84%
And we're doing the
FDA studies to get them

00:59:21.099 --> 00:59:24.644 align:middle line:84%
a status called Generally
Recognized As Safe, or GRAS.

00:59:24.644 --> 00:59:26.271 align:middle line:84%
So they're under
investigation now.

00:59:26.271 --> 00:59:31.234 align:middle line:84%
The ones on the market now
would be the ketone mineral salt

00:59:31.234 --> 00:59:36.323 align:middle line:84%
supplements in combination with
medium-chain triglyceride fats.

00:59:36.323 --> 00:59:40.118 align:middle line:84%
And the combination of a ketone
and a mineral salt, which

00:59:40.118 --> 00:59:44.039 align:middle line:84%
is essentially a ketone with
sodium, potassium, magnesium

00:59:44.039 --> 00:59:46.500 align:middle line:84%
combined with it-- so
it's delivering minerals

00:59:46.500 --> 00:59:48.710 align:middle line:84%
to your body in
addition to ketones.

00:59:48.710 --> 00:59:52.255 align:middle line:84%
And we combine it with
medium-chain triglyceride

00:59:52.255 --> 00:59:53.215 align:middle line:90%
powder.

00:59:53.215 --> 00:59:57.052 align:middle line:84%
And the fat enhances our
own ketone production

00:59:57.052 --> 01:00:00.180 align:middle line:84%
by beta oxidation
of liver and also

01:00:00.180 --> 01:00:02.724 align:middle line:84%
functions as sort of a
carrier for the ketones.

01:00:02.724 --> 01:00:06.978 align:middle line:84%
So it in a way kind of
delays absorption and helps

01:00:06.978 --> 01:00:10.982 align:middle line:84%
increase the sustained
effect of ketones over time,

01:00:10.982 --> 01:00:12.108 align:middle line:90%
adding a little bit of fat.

01:00:12.108 --> 01:00:14.236 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So would this be
