01:00:15.695 --> 01:00:16.488 align:middle line:90%
>>D'AGOSTINO: Yeah.

01:00:16.488 --> 01:00:19.491 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: In general, just for
your overall health profile.

01:00:19.491 --> 01:00:23.161 align:middle line:84%
>>D'AGOSTINO: Yeah, I think it's
like medium-chain triglyceride

01:00:23.161 --> 01:00:25.956 align:middle line:90%
