01:00:25.956 --> 01:00:33.672 align:middle line:84%
It's a supplement that can
enhance nutritional ketosis.

01:00:33.672 --> 01:00:37.300 align:middle line:84%
So you could be on a diet that's
much more liberal with protein

01:00:37.300 --> 01:00:39.845 align:middle line:84%
