01:00:44.641 --> 01:00:47.853 align:middle line:84%
So you get all the
therapeutic benefits

01:00:47.853 --> 01:00:50.897 align:middle line:84%
with circumventing some of
the dietary restriction,

01:00:50.897 --> 01:00:52.566 align:middle line:84%
classically associated
with achieving

01:00:52.566 --> 01:00:53.525 align:middle line:90%
that therapeutic state.

